query: INSERT INTO adminPermissions (userId, balanceManagement, userManagement, permissionManagement, memberManagement, staffManagement, status, createdBy) SELECT id, true, true, true, true, false, 'active', 1 FROM users WHERE role = 'staff_admin' AND id NOT IN (SELECT userId FROM adminPermissions);
